---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="About Kamadhenu Goushala">

<!-- Temple Hero -->

<section class="temple-hero">

<div class="container hero-center">

<h1>Kamadhenu Goushala</h1>

<p class="hero-mantra">
Vande Goumataram
</p>

<p class="hero-desc">
A sacred space dedicated to protecting indigenous cows and preserving the
spiritual traditions of Bharath.
</p>

</div>

</section>


<!-- Temple Divider -->

<div class="temple-divider"></div>


<!-- About Section -->

<section class="section">

<div class="container">

<div class="about-grid">

<img src="/images/about/goushala.jpg" class="about-img">

<div>

<h2>About Our Goushala</h2>

<p>
Kamadhenu Goushala is dedicated to protecting indigenous Indian cow breeds
and promoting sustainable agriculture practices rooted in our ancient
traditions.
</p>

<p>
Established on <strong>24th August 2020</strong> at
<strong>Kavadi, Virajpet Taluk, Kodagu (Coorg)</strong>, the goushala serves
as a sanctuary for sacred cows and a center for spreading awareness about
gau seva.
</p>

</div>

</div>

</div>

</section>


<!-- Spiritual Quote -->

<section class="quote-section">

<div class="container">

<p class="quote">

“The place we refer to as home deserves to be recognized as such only if
it is filled with devotion and respect for Guru and Gau Mata.”

</p>

<p class="quote-author">

Jagadguru Shankaracharya  
Sri Sri Raghaveshwara Bharati Mahaswamiji

</p>

</div>

</section>


<!-- Timeline -->

<section class="section timeline-section">

<div class="container">

<h2 class="section-title">
Our Journey
</h2>

<div class="timeline">

<div class="timeline-item">

<h3>2020</h3>

<p>
Kamadhenu Goushala was established with the mission of protecting
indigenous cow breeds.
</p>

</div>

<div class="timeline-item">

<h3>2021</h3>

<p>
The goushala expanded and began producing traditional cow-based products.
</p>

</div>

<div class="timeline-item">

<h3>2023</h3>

<p>
Awareness programs started to educate farmers about indigenous cow breeds.
</p>

</div>

<div class="timeline-item">

<h3>Today</h3>

<p>
The goushala now shelters around 60–70 cows and continues serving the
community.
</p>

</div>

</div>

</div>

</section>


